<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <title>Confirm the <c:splice lquery="(text title)"/> settings for <c:splice lquery="(text host)"/></title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Confirm the <c:splice lquery="(text title)"/> settings for <c:splice lquery="(text host)"/></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="main">
      <p>
        Hello, <c:splice lquery="(text recipient)"/>. You have recently added a new email host. Please click the below link to confirm that it is working.
      </p>
      <a class="block" lquery="(attr :href link) (text link)">URL</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        &copy; <div lquery="(time T)">2019</div> <c:splice lquery="(text copyright)">Shirakumo</c:splice><br/>
        Running on <a href="https://shirakumo.org/projects/courier">Courier <c:splice lquery="(text version)">0.0.0</c:splice></a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
